{
  "stem": "617.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That when we first arrived to Stutthof, the first selection, when we were not taken, we hadn't-- they didn't send us to the infirmary yet, because that selection, they were very selective who they are taking.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they didn't care so much, you know, that they're leaving so many behind.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And our friends who we were with in Latvia at the time came from our country, and we became very good friends.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were selected to go, and they were two sisters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we wanted to go so much with them, and we couldn't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They wouldn't let us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were the SS already guarding them, that nobody else should get into their group.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I-- I, my sister, somehow or other, we managed to push into that group.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were standing with them, just before they were leaving, and they counted that there were two more.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they counted again, and there were two more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then somehow, whether they noticed, or somebody told, they grabbed me out of line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The SS, it was a woman SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She beat the daylight out of me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Not my sister, me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "She beat me so hard that my sister thought that this is the end, that I'll never be able to get up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I did get up.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
